{"tid":1842810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有無人記得武漢大學生失蹤事件","createTime":"2020-01-26T02:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T20:36:19.000Z","uid":40478,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a5c24073e07143e20df4570271886bb6c645b15a","tid":1842810,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:37:34.000Z","msg":"醬油比支那刪到得番大紀元：<br />\n武漢數十名大學生神祕失蹤 官方為何急「闢謠」<br />\n更新: 2017年09月29日 8:33 PM<br />\n<br />\n然後武漢p4實驗室係2017年開始運作<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1152978f111cfcadeab3d947e381e6b9917833","tid":1842810,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecaa7536eee43bf7ab7392719b2a4b182a17951b","tid":1842810,"uid":265316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:40:42.000Z","msg":"其實這隻病毒<br />\n我覺得係專殺年輕人<br />\n只不過年輕人衛生意識高<br />\n所以感染率冇咁高<br />\n死亡率亦冇咁高<br />\n<br />\n所以我好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918b3c5284e2d99ae4257bb484008f427f2e4da8","tid":1842810,"uid":313514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T02:41:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c2b03c59f1a8546e5211375cad74ffcb54c1de2","tid":1842810,"uid":40250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:16:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/11e3QmSnFK4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F11e3QmSnFK4&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=f972f878\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/11e3QmSnFK4</a>"},{"pid":"8b4ec30c8fe5b7f7fefcb56fa7b2898afa9885d1","tid":1842810,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:16:33.000Z","msg":"#武漢大學生再爆失蹤<br />\n<br />\n2017年下半年武漢失蹤大學生在媒體的曝光之下，引起各界關注，之後事件逐漸沉寂。<br />\n<br />\n2018年下半年，再次爆發武漢大學生失蹤事件，仍然由於警方的不作為，事情毫無頭緒，失蹤者家屬們陷入絕望中。<br />\n<br />\n潘英豪，今年19歲，身高1.80米，武漢市孝感區安陸市趙棚鎮陶廟村人，武漢警官職業學院大二學生。2018年12月22日晚上在武昌區臨江大道平湖門下出租車後失蹤至今。<br />\n<br />\n王女士表示，在兒子失蹤後的三個月當中全部都是家屬自己調查監控、搜尋線索，然後告訴警方，讓警方去調查。<br />\n<br />\n「12月22日下午五點半接了一個QQ或者微信電話讓他走的，這個人很重要，但是（警方）不立案不給查，說我兒子不是刑事案件。如果當時報案的話，當時就可以攔截下來，現在一推再推，說案件太小了。我都懷疑我兒子沒了，要不然怎麼可能手機幾個月沒用。據有關方面人反映，QQ訊息只能保留六個月，現在都四個月了。」王女士氣憤地說。<br />\n<br />\n王女士還說：「校方態度更不好，不協助我們。（家屬）想讓他們幫我們請求立案，（但校方）到現在都反映不到上面去，把這事推得一乾二淨。」<br />\n<br />\n王女士現在非常無奈，不知道如何去尋找自己的兒子。<br />\n<br />\n據家屬們初步統計，目前已知的在武漢失蹤的大學生有三十餘名，至今僅有一名失蹤的大學生找到遺體。"},{"pid":"366d42c8edd8d64e05acf150c0c1bedf057078dd","tid":1842810,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/missing-09292017074101.html/ampRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fmissing-09292017074101.html%2FampRFA&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=167412b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/missing-09292017074101.html/ampRFA</a>"},{"pid":"75f6702a40b683b5e3bdcd029897e1c27e2e12ea","tid":1842810,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:20:35.000Z","msg":"睇番時間，同P4實險室時間相似"},{"pid":"33a933828c9b24ab1ac6acb741b4f6b1ea6337fc","tid":1842810,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:20:46.000Z","msg":"武漢人真係慘"},{"pid":"c064c662fd15f7545bc186641a9bcc9087e8fd0f","tid":1842810,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60608715aa00fce2dab66e3ed08c134e9d3ed2ce","tid":1842810,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af36e35d